"1 1/2 pounds Brussels sprouts, trimmed and thinly sliced (about 9 cups)","2  medium sweet potatoes (about 1 lb. total), peeled and cut into 1/2-inch cubes (about 2 3/4 cups)","1  medium onion, sliced (about 2 1/4 cups)","1/4 cup extra-virgin olive oil, plus more for baking sheets","1/2 teaspoon crushed red pepper flakes","  Salt","2 tablespoons cider vinegar","2 teaspoons Dijon mustard","1 teaspoon honey"